a little cabin, with a snowstorm raging outside,

11
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:24,510
Inside,

12
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,760
by the fire,

13
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:28,010
I wasn't so scared anymore.

14
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,920
It was like

15
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:33,100
no matter how big the world is,

16
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:34,820
there's always a place

17
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,250
where I can feel warmth.

18
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:42,880
Thank you

19
