26
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,700
There's nothing much to say about it.

27
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,310
No, that won't do.

28
00:01:07,310 --> 00:01:08,970
We can't be so casual about it.

29
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:15,640
Make a wish.

30
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,020
Let's forget about it.

31
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:20,310
Why?

32
00:01:20,590 --> 00:01:21,310
Don't you

33
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:23,570
want the Jingcai Basketball Team to win?

34
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:26,840
If making wishes really worked,

35
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:30,530
wouldn’t all the awful things in the world

36
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:32,430
just disappear?

37
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,640
Not all wishes can come true,

38
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:39,800
but at least, they bring a little hope into our lives.

39
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,130
Instead of waiting endlessly,

40
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:44,350
why not

41
00:01:44,789 --> 00:01:45,789
just take action?

42
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,180
Just make one wish.

43
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:49,840
Alright.

44
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:52,210
Then I’ll share half of mine with you.

45
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,150
Really?

46
00:02:07,050 --> 00:02:11,990
♪ I knew I had a few problems with the wrong ones ♪

47
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:19,680
♪ I don't even wanna think about it anyway ♪

48
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:28,230
♪ I flew away from these issues, now I got you ♪

49
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:35,730
♪ I don't even wanna worry 'bout yesterday ♪

50
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,760
That was my wish just now.

51
00:02:39,490 --> 00:02:43,720
♪ Was sick of waiting, lying there for days ♪

52
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:47,540
♪ Wishing for the seasons to change ♪

53
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,250
♪ But now you see the best of me ♪

54
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,500
I'll go clean up first.

55
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:16,710
You

56
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,370
seem to have a message.

57
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,570
Jiang Bohan!

58
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:29,610
I got the lottery.

59
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:30,670
Congratulations.

60
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,150
Let's celebrate then.

61
00:03:33,150 --> 00:03:33,560
Okay.

62
