74
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:27,250
[Close to You]

75
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,480
[Episode 23, Half of My Wish for You]

76
00:05:53,610 --> 00:05:54,580
I'm done crying.

77
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:00,950
You have a tissue?

78
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,150
Just now, Qin Siyao said

79
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:11,000
all I ever do is act cute,

80
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,630
fangirl all the time,

81
00:06:13,090 --> 00:06:14,750
and constantly hang around you guys;

82
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,150
that I’m super annoying.

83
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,810
No one would ever like someone like me.

84
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,680
Do you think so too?

85
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:24,560
I...

86
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:29,250
I think you just didn't perform well.

87
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:31,190
You could have won the argument.

88
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:34,110
You think I could have won?

89
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:35,430
Of course.

90
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,080
What she said isn’t true.

91
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:40,750
There’s no way no one would like you.

92
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,720
Your mom and dad,

93
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,480
your grandpas,

94
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,000
and grandmas,

95
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,120
Mingxi

96
00:06:49,890 --> 00:06:50,600
and me...

97
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,360
What do you mean?

98
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:02,870
Are you...

99
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,080
Are you confessing to me?

100
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:27,260
Say that again.

101
00:07:35,659 --> 00:07:37,860
Do you remember when we first met?

102
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,610
I saw you on the basketball court.

103
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,880
You smiled, and you looked so cute.

104
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,270
Your eyes were big

105
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,760
and sparkly,

106
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,630
like stars.

107
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:49,430
Later,

108
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:52,600
you followed me in the library.

109
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,270
You found out my secret

110
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,600
and insisted I see a doctor,

111
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:01,150
that I get my leg checked.

112
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,240
I’m really grateful

113
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,960
to have had you by my side all this time.

114
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,630
You accompanied me to the hospital,

115
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,290
and to acupuncture sessions.

116
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,360
At that dinner,

117
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,560
you kept drinking for me,

118
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,750
glass after glass.

119
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,370
At that time, I felt

120
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:23,760
quite sorry for you.

121
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:29,360
I hadn’t done a good job of protecting you,

122
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,220
and even let you

123
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:31,890
drink so much on my behalf.

124
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,559
You've been by my side

125
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:36,870
all this time,

126
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:39,450
and it's made me really happy.

127
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,970
It’s also helped me know more of who you truly are.

128
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,040
Wang Chunian,

129
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:51,600
I like you.

130
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:54,450
♪ Fake a new love till you find it ♪

131
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:57,710
♪ Living a life now it's gone ♪

132
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,600
Will you be with me?

133
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:01,350
♪ I'm here with her coz she looks like you ♪

134
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:03,380
♪ But I guess I'd take anyone ♪

135
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,930
You said yes?

136
00:09:04,930 --> 00:09:07,210
♪ Your words fill these empty sapces ♪

137
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:07,960
Chen Sujie,

138
00:09:08,070 --> 00:09:10,710
♪ You're alone when you're in a crowd ♪

139
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:10,840
This is

140
00:09:11,210 --> 00:09:13,210
the first time someone has confessed to me.

141
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:14,460
♪ Wake up with her and pretend it's you ♪

142
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,610
♪ I nearly said your name aloud ♪

143
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,400
Alright.

144
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:21,370
♪ So I bury it, cover it in dirt ♪

145
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,240
Don't cry.

146
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,480
Actually, this is also my first time

147
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:24,520
♪ But then I'll know I'll make, wrong decisions that'll hurt ♪

148
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,680
confessing to a girl.

149
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,150
Really?

150
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:27,910
♪ But I can't bear the fact you've moved on ♪

151
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:30,890
♪ That I got to feel I never be gone ♪

152
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,950
You're not choosing anyone else from the basketball team?

153
00:09:31,950 --> 00:09:35,430
♪ And I can't stop rereading your texts ♪

154
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,080
Really?

155
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:38,950
♪ You'll always be more than just an existence ♪

156
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:42,060
♪ I can't bear the fact you'd move on ♪

157
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:45,440
♪ That I got to feel you never be gone ♪

158
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:50,410
♪ I see you getting stronger, on the things you took from me ♪

159
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:49,550
Then what's my next

160
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,630
wish?

161
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:53,510
♪ I'm no longer, who I used to be ♪

162
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:54,750
You fulfilled the wish I had before graduation.

163
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:56,780
♪ You took everything that hurts to lose ♪

164
00:09:56,810 --> 00:10:00,040
♪ I can only heal with someone like you ♪

165
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:03,550
♪ I can be stronger, thinking the hands I feel are yours ♪

166
00:10:03,590 --> 00:10:06,960
♪ Yes, it's wrong but, it might be the only cure ♪

167
00:10:07,050 --> 00:10:09,790
♪ Gotta find a love that's brand new ♪

168
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:13,470
♪ Gotta find a love that's brand new ♪

169
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:17,140
♪ But only if it's someone like you ♪

170
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,960
[The place is empty now. I'm moving out today. I'm sorry. You don't have to avoid me anymore.]

171
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:28,550
What are you looking at,

172
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:29,480
with that frown?

173
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:30,800
Thank you.

174
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,490
Your favorite—Flat White.

175
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,270
It's still so delicious.

176
00:10:40,590 --> 00:10:41,140
Yes.

177
00:10:41,610 --> 00:10:44,140
After you left, I tried it in other places too.

178
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,550
But

179
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:47,300
the one you brought me to still tastes the best.

180
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,100
Do you know why I like to drink Flat White?

181
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:51,160
Of course.

182
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,590
Flat White only uses the richest part of the espresso from the first extraction,

183
00:10:54,590 --> 00:10:55,230
so the flavor’s better

184
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:56,360
and it has less milk.

185
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,710
Cutting back on dairy

186
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,240
is good for your skin,

187
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,320
and

188
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,200
the foam is lighter,

189
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,550
so it doesn’t stick to your lips —

190
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:04,140
it’s more elegant

191
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:04,710
to drink.

192
00:11:04,930 --> 00:11:06,480
That’s why it suits you.

193
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:11,290
I remember you didn't use to like coffee.

194
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,950
Well, you liked it,

195
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,270
so I looked into it.

196
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:17,830
Then why keep drinking it if you didn’t like it?

197
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:25,020
I didn't like it at first,

198
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:27,010
because it tastes bitter.

199
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,410
But the more I drank it,

200
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,630
the more I started to like it.

201
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,000
So you see,

202
00:11:36,810 --> 00:11:38,480
forming a new habit...

203
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:40,230
It only takes twenty-one days.

204
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:49,310
You haven’t seen your therapist in a while.

205
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:50,650
Are you doing okay now?

206
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:55,070
Did you two keep in touch after the breakup?

207
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,800
It’s been two years.

208
00:11:58,810 --> 00:12:00,210
We haven’t spoken since.

209
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:01,390
Now,

210
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:04,630
I don't want to contact her anymore.

211
00:12:06,810 --> 00:12:08,810
Actually, I kind of want to meet her.

212
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,120
Why?

213
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:12,600
To thank her.

214
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:14,790
If it weren’t for her, I wouldn’t have met you.

215
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:16,320
Finding joy in sorrow, huh?

216
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,670
This is

217
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:18,320
called

218
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:21,280
looking for the silver lining.

219
00:12:26,370 --> 00:12:29,130
I thought you went abroad to live your happily-ever-after

220
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:30,390
and forgot all about us.

221
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,510
I just went abroad.

222
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:33,170
It's not like I have dementia.

223
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,840
I really envy you.

224
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:40,440
You're so young, and you've already found someone worth loving for a lifetime.

225
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,700
A lifetime is too long.

226
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:44,550
Living well in the moment is enough.

227
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,080
My birthday is coming up.

228
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,510
What are you getting me?

229
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,120
How about me?

230
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:55,970
You little rascal, how dare you joke with me?

231
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,520
If you don't like it,

232
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,380
I won't give myself as a gift then.

233
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:06,870
Mingxi,

234
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:09,150
take Jingchu to stay somewhere else for a couple of days.

235
00:13:09,150 --> 00:13:09,840
Go now.

236
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:10,750
Why?

237
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,910
Why so sudden?

238
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,670
Those debt collectors are getting bolder.

239
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,930
I'm worried about you.

240
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,800
I'm afraid they'll come and cause trouble for you.

241
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:18,290
Mom,

242
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,030
don't worry.

243
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:20,080
We live in a society governed by law now.

244
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,680
They won't do anything to me.

245
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,360
No.

246
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,570
Listen to me.

247
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,390
Leave now.

248
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,070
Don't worry about us.

249
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,600
Remember to come back early.

250
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,000
Okay.

251
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:29,710
Mom,

252
00:13:29,730 --> 00:13:30,660
I’ll hang up now.

253
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:31,790
Stop right there!

254
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:32,920
Why are you running?

255
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:34,010
Stop!

256
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,390
Yu Mingxi.

257
00:13:40,570 --> 00:13:41,120
Who are you?

258
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:41,620
Get in the car.

259
00:13:41,620 --> 00:13:42,220
Don't run!

260
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:42,870
Stop!

261
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:58,910
She got away.

262
00:14:06,230 --> 00:14:08,630
So you're Jiang Bohan's senior.

263
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:09,440
Yes, I am.

264
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:11,200
I also graduated from Jingcai College.

265
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,030
Who were those people just now?

266
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:14,720
They're

267
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,150
debt collectors.

268
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,120
But,

269
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,200
Senior,

270
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,810
why were you at my doorstep?

271
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:25,000
I came here specifically to see you.

272
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:29,520
I want to ask for your help in persuading Jiang Bohan

273
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:32,320
to accept the Blue Wolves' offer to play overseas.

274
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:34,720
Blue Wolves?

275
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:40,750
Jiang Bohan has been playing basketball since elementary school.

276
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:43,350
He was rated a four-star player in high school,

277
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:47,110
and after graduation, he got an invitation from the Blue Wolves.

278
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,370
Back then, he had a bright future ahead of him.

279
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:57,240
He must have told you about Boyang, right?

280
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,240
Since then,

281
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:01,170
he's been like a different person.

282
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,400
He never mentioned going abroad again,

283
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,480
and even turned down the offer.

284
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:08,330
Thankfully, his mom managed to stop him in time.

285
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:10,550
It's been over two years.

286
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,660
It's time to move forward.

287
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,790
Actually, ever since he met you,

288
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:19,320
he’s become a lot more open.

289
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:22,490
I know you're very important to him.

290
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,800
If you truly care about him,

291
00:15:25,190 --> 00:15:26,790
please help me persuade him.

292
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,440
But...

293
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:31,220
Would he

294
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,710
even listen to me?

295
00:15:34,710 --> 00:15:36,140
I've never seen

296
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,640
him care this much about any other girl.

297
00:15:40,510 --> 00:15:42,150
After Boyang left,

298
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:45,760
he stopped celebrating his birthday altogether.

299
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:48,800
But he was willing to blow out candles with you.

300
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:52,600
That means you’ve already found a place in his heart.

301
00:15:58,630 --> 00:16:00,050
Go abroad with him.

302
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,850
But...

303
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:02,480
Senior,

304
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,060
you know about

305
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,650
my family's situation.

306
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,870
So you're working so hard

307
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:10,110
just to pay off debts?

308
00:16:11,950 --> 00:16:12,430
Senior,

309
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:14,280
please promise me you’ll keep this a secret.

310
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:16,030
You absolutely can’t tell Jiang Bohan.

311
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:16,760
Don't worry,

312
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,040
I won't say anything.

313
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,440
Actually, if you have financial difficulties,

314
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:22,500
I can also try to find a way to help you.

315
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:23,550
No need.

316
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:24,840
This is my

317
00:16:25,110 --> 00:16:26,150
family’s problem.

318
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:26,950
I still want to

319
00:16:27,150 --> 00:16:28,150
handle it myself.

320
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:29,750
You don't have to be so polite with me.

321
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,310
It's not like I'm asking you not to pay me back.

322
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:33,710
I'm just waiving the interest, that's all.

323
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,750
You're so young, yet already

324
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:36,750
burdened by life.

325
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,060
Even I feel for you.

326
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,430
Let alone Jiang Bohan.

327
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,610
Or,

328
00:16:43,850 --> 00:16:45,520
if you need someone to talk to,

329
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,600
you can come to me.

330
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,480
Trust me,

331
00:16:47,670 --> 00:16:49,930
I'm a professional emotional dumpster.

332
00:17:09,630 --> 00:17:11,849
You’ve already found your way into his heart.

333
00:17:11,849 --> 00:17:13,130
Go abroad with him.

334
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:15,030
Do me a favor.

335
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:17,510
Please don't break his heart.

336
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:45,390
[Close to You]
